@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

box "Backend System (Sistema AIT)" #LightBlue
    participant "HTTP Request" as HttpRequest
    participant "Route" as Route
    participant "Controller" as Controller
    participant "DTO" as Dto
    participant "Service Interface" as ServiceInterface
    participant "Service Implementation" as ServiceImpl
    box "Persistence" #LightGreen
        participant "Data Model" as DataModel
        participant "Aggregate" as Aggregate
        participant "Value Object" as ValueObject
        participant "Entity" as Entity
        participant "Repository Interface" as RepoInterface
        participant "Repository Implementation" as RepoImpl
    end box
end box

HttpRequest -> Route : 1.1: POST /api/qualifications
activate HttpRequest
Route -> Controller : 1.2: Invoke CreateQualification
activate Route
Controller -> Dto : 1.3: Map request body (CreateQualificationDto)
activate Controller
Dto --> Controller : 1.4: Mapped data
deactivate Dto
Controller -> ServiceInterface : 1.5: CreateAsync(dto)
activate ServiceInterface
ServiceInterface -> ServiceImpl : 1.6: Delegate to implementation
activate ServiceImpl
ServiceImpl -> Aggregate : 1.7: Create aggregate (new Qualification)
activate Aggregate
Aggregate -> ValueObject : 1.7.1: Create value objects (Code, Name, Desc VOs)
activate ValueObject
ValueObject --> Aggregate : 1.7.2: Value objects created
deactivate ValueObject
Aggregate -> Entity : 1.7.3: Create entity instance
activate Entity
Entity --> Aggregate : 1.7.4: Entity created
deactivate Entity
Aggregate --> ServiceImpl : 1.7.5: Aggregate created (qualification instance)
deactivate Aggregate
ServiceImpl -> RepoInterface : 1.8: AddAsync(qualification)
activate RepoInterface
RepoInterface -> RepoImpl : 1.9: Delegate to implementation
activate RepoImpl
RepoImpl -> DataModel : 1.9.1: Map aggregate to data model (DbContext.Add)
activate DataModel
DataModel --> RepoImpl : 1.9.2: Data model mapped/tracked
deactivate DataModel
RepoImpl --> RepoInterface : 1.10: Data ready to persist
deactivate RepoImpl
RepoInterface --> ServiceImpl : 1.11: Data ready to persist
deactivate RepoInterface
ServiceImpl -> DataModel : 1.11.1: SaveChangesAsync()
activate DataModel
DataModel --> ServiceImpl : 1.11.2: Changes saved
deactivate DataModel
ServiceImpl --> ServiceInterface : 1.12: Response data (QualificationDto mapped)
deactivate ServiceImpl
ServiceInterface --> Controller : 1.13: Response data (QualificationDto)
deactivate ServiceInterface
Controller --> HttpRequest : 1.14: HTTP 201 Created
deactivate Controller
deactivate Route
HttpRequest --> : 1.15: HTTP Response
deactivate HttpRequest

@enduml